Would you like that ?

498
00:58:25,000 --> 00:58:27,070
Remove your hand.

499
00:58:27,160 --> 00:58:30,118
Perhaps, Your Grace,
we shall think on it, but...

500
00:58:30,200 --> 00:58:34,159
- l am deeply religious.
- But l am very religious, too.

501
00:58:34,240 --> 00:58:36,993
Very religious, yes !

