may be recovered from heresy.

508
00:59:31,760 --> 00:59:34,752
Prayers may not be sufficient.

509
00:59:34,840 --> 00:59:37,149
l will ask for guidance in this matter.

510
00:59:37,240 --> 00:59:39,595
But do not despair.

511
00:59:39,680 --> 00:59:45,516
Was it not truly said
that the righteous shall inherit the earth ?

512
00:59:56,800 --> 00:59:58,756
Such piercing eyes !

513
00:59:58,840 --> 01:00:00,796
And very indiscreet !

514
01:00:32,200 --> 01:00:35,829
My true love has my heart

515
01:00:36,840 --> 01:00:38,796
and l have hers.

516
01:00:39,200 --> 01:00:41,156
My heart in me

517
01:00:41,240 --> 01:00:43,595
keeps her and me in one.

518
01:00:43,800 --> 01:00:48,271
My heart in her,
her thoughts and senses guide.

519
01:00:48,360 --> 01:00:50,510
She loves my heart

520
01:00:51,080 --> 01:00:53,753
for once it was her own.

521
01:00:54,800 --> 01:00:56,756
l cherish hers

522
01:00:58,200 --> 01:01:00,953
